    Load the library.

    library(pdcsync)

    Simulate two time series

    N <- 1000

t1 <- arima.sim(model = list(ar = 0.2), n = N)

# t2 is later than t1; t1 leads
t2 <- c(t1[4:(length(t1))], 0, 0, 0) + rnorm(N, 0, 0.001)

# no synchrony between 200 and 400
t2[200:400] <- runif(201, 0, 1)

    sync <- pdcsync(t1, t2)
